    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! It's the perfect daily driver that still looks great on the road and runs like a charm. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
